{"tid":1042133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又一單] 女子進食河豚後懷疑中毒入院　現時情況嚴重","createTime":"2019-03-01T10:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T09:50:50.000Z","uid":51271,"like":486,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"636c8eafd9d5a48616e7bd3ff2deb8efafef2ee6","tid":1042133,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:46:39.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心表示，一名女子進食河豚後懷疑中毒，出現口唇麻痺、全身無力、嘔吐和呼吸衰竭，現時情況嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n事主69歲，昨日食用由丈夫在本港捕獲並經烹煮的河豚作晚餐，感到不適，到天水圍醫院急症室求醫，其後轉送屯門醫院，需在深切治療部接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心發言人表示，河豚毒素是一種毒性強烈的水溶性神經毒素，而且耐熱，不會在烹煮、風乾或冷藏過程中被分解，可影響中樞神經系統，嚴重可能會致命，現時並無已知的解毒劑或抗毒素可分解河豚毒素，中心建議市民應避免購買及自行宰洗河豚進食。　"},{"pid":"edd491de52db24c1087d6f9eea19bb42b76ca314","tid":1042133,"uid":121255,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f33dd1eee2571f331e484f70d135ee36670f7b","tid":1042133,"uid":188,"like":735,"dislike":1,"score":734,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:47:30.000Z","msg":"由丈夫在本港捕獲並經烹煮的河豚作晚餐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592c3f9340240c852cc717c8272ce1fd70480f4d","tid":1042133,"uid":110858,"like":5,"dislike":212,"score":-207,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:47:54.000Z","msg":"豚肉成日都食架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9478b3270e7d6b4f3c5978cab66520148f1ba425","tid":1042133,"uid":23993,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8559e84b514a2188d0912b270cee9e83f6cfb483","tid":1042133,"uid":51271,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T1